Package com.hoddmimes.distributor

Class DistributorErrorEvent

java.lang.Object
com.hoddmimes.distributor.DistributorEvent
com.hoddmimes.distributor.DistributorErrorEvent
Direct Known Subclasses:
DistributorCommunicationErrorEvent, DistributorConnectionClosedErrorEvent, DistributorNaggingErrorEvent, DistributorRetransmissionNAKErrorEvent, DistributorTooManyRetransmissionRetriesErrorEvent
public abstract class DistributorErrorEvent
extends DistributorEvent
This class serve is an abstract class and server as base for all application events being of fatal nature. All events inheriting from this class indicate that the event is an error event and that the error is fatal.
